txt.en: Wild men from Dunland have set up camp along the Fords of Isen, seething with a violent hatred for the horse-lords.\n\nYou should defeat the Dunlendings at their camp atop the cliff overlooking the river.
Invading Dunlendings can be found in their war-camp overlooking the Fords of Isen in the Westfold.\n\nYou should defeat Dunlending invaders.
You have defeated a number of Dunlendings at the Fords of Isen, but the true danger marches by the tens of thousands towards Helm's Deep.
